E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Assholes don't know how much it's worth. They're screwing it up on the beach at Firefly.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~有一群不识货的臭傻逼，在Firefly的海滩上瞎搞。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_C_NA
~z~Fuck it, we're on.
~z~If I could use my legs, I'd jump for joy Johnny boy. Later on, Brother.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~要不是腿瘸了，我就高兴得跳起来了，Johnny。之后见，兄弟。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_C_GA
~z~Hey, Angus. Know any bikes that need to be liberated from their owners?
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，Angus。有没有需要脱离车主魔爪的摩托？

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~The bike's right there for you, brother. No problem.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~你要的摩托已经备好了，兄弟。没问题。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~ I'm glad we got you to do the acquiring.
E1J3_B_RD
~z~Hellfury delivered, my brother.
~z~Good as done.
~z~Your man's gonna get some bad news, Angus. Tell him for me, will you?
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~有一个坏消息要跟你老板说，Angus。替我转告他好吗？

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Angus, I got a feeling there might be a bike you're looking for.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~Angus，你是不是又看上了哪辆摩托啊？

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_B_WA
~z~Bike's outside the house where you wanted it, man.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~摩托按你说的停在会所外面了，兄弟。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Tell me where I can find a bike and it's yours, Angus.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~告诉我车在哪里，我帮你弄来，Angus。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Don't worry about it. Stay safe.
E1J3_C_IA
~z~It's yours.
~z~ You and your man have now got yourselves a PCJ, man.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~你和你老板要的PCJ已经拿到了。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_B_NB
E1J3_B_RB
~z~Fuck if I can pronounce it, but a Ha-ha-coochie-koo is now in your possession, Angus.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~这名儿真念不来，那辆哈哈库奇库现在是你的了，Angus。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_B_MA
E1J3_C_OB
~z~All cool, Johnny. Later on.
E1J3_C_AA
~z~Shit man, you could have told me I'd be driving a dirt bike. Anyways, I got that Sanchez for you.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，你早点说这次是山地车啊。总之，我拿到Sanchez了。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Guy's riding it round Chinatown.
E1J3_B_NA
~z~You ain't perfect, Johnny. None of us are. Don't worry about it.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~人无完人，Johnny。我们都一样。别担心。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Heading there now.
~z~Angus, man, I'm sorry but shit got fucked up and I couldn't get that bike.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~Angus，兄弟，很抱歉事情搞砸了，我没弄到车。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~I'm here for the bike, not your life, so be cool.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~我要的是车，不是你的命，老实点。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~No problem. See you, man.
E1J3_C_LA
E1J3_B_RA
~z~Some Deadbeats left it outside that liquor store on Dillon Street.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~几个死妈天使把车停在Dillon街的酒水商店门外。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_B_SA
~z~Brother, Man, something's come up. I can't get the bike for you. Another time.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~兄弟，出了点意外。我没法替你弄车了。下次再说吧。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~There's too many assholes in this city on bikes, my man. Which one can I deprive of his ride?
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~城里骑摩托车的傻逼太多了，老兄。我该抢哪个人的车？

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Hey, your contact better still want that bike 'cause I got it for him.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，你的上家最好不要跑单，因为我已经得手了。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~I'm cracking open a celebratory Piswasser already. Too cool, brother man.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~我已经开好尿汤啤庆祝了。干得漂亮，好兄弟。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_B_XA
~z~Too bad, brother, but that guy won't be getting his hands on that bike today.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~太糟了，兄弟，但你老板今天见不到车了。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_B_RG
~z~One Wolfsbane ready and waiting for you, my brother.
E1J3_C_EA
~z~Fuck it, man. It ain't like that was the only bike in the city.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~操他妈的。反正城里多的是摩托车。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_C_HA
~z~The bike's all parked up and waiting, man.
E1J3_B_RH
E1J3_B_VA
E1J3_B_TA
~z~Brother man, tell me where I can find a bike and I'll bring it right to you.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~好兄弟，告诉我哪里能找到摩托，我给你搞过来。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_B_YA
~z~How 'bout that, man? I happened to come across a Nightblade right where you said.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~怎么样，兄弟？我碰巧在你说的地方看到一辆Nightblade。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_B_RC
~z~Cool, Johnny, cool. I'll let the man know what went down.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~没事，Johnny，没事的。我会跟他说明情况的。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_B_PA
~z~Brother man, we're going to get paid. Don't get too fucked up.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~兄弟，又有钱进账了。别乱挥霍。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Bike's outside of the clubhouse, now all you need to do is get it out the country, Angus.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~车已经在会所外面了，接下来只需要出口国外了，Angus。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, Angus, I'm in the bike stealing mood. Where am I gonna be able to find one?
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，Angus，我想偷摩托车了。你说去哪儿偷一辆好？

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~All good.
~z~We've got one for you, old friend. Just try to save me the hassle and deliver it this time.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~之前也找过你了，老朋友。这次就让我省点心，把车弄到手吧。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_B_ZA
~z~Angus, man. She's parked up outside the House.
~z~Hey Angus, hate to do this to a brother, but I can't go get you that bike. Sorry.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，Angus，虽然不想这样，但我不能你搞到那辆摩托了。抱歉。

E1J3AUD.original: SFX_PAUSE_120
~z~I hate to split up a pair of lovebirds, but there's a couple taking it for a spin round Middle Park.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~我讨厌棒打鸳鸯，但是有对情侣正骑着它在中心公园兜风。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_C_JA
~z~I've got something, Johnny. Please, for me, can you make sure it gets here?
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~是有目标，Johnny。给兄弟个面子，这次能保证弄到手吗？

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~What's up?
~z~That's cool, Brother. The man will just have to wait.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~没事的，兄弟。就让老板多等会儿吧。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~There's an Angel motorcycle ready for export, man. That was my end of the deal.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~这辆Angel摩托已经准备好出口了。我这边完成了。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Cool.
~z~Hey.
~z~That bike ain't AOD property no more.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~那辆摩托不再属于死妈天使了。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_B_RI
~z~Got the NRG 900, man. Do what you will.
E1J3_B_UA
~z~Hey, man.
~z~Your paper route's over, man. Get off the bike.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~你的送报工作该下班了，老兄。快滚下来。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_B_RE
~z~Man, oh, man, that's what I wanted to hear. Stay safe.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~兄弟啊，兄弟，就知道你靠得住。保重。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Big group of Deadbeats are taking it for a run down the old Alderney freeway.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~一大群死妈天使正骑着车在Alderney的高速上兜风。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~You got your Daemon, man. Put a stamp on it and ship that mother.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~Daemon到手了，兄弟。贴好邮票以后就装箱发货吧。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Stop jacking up my new ride, fuckhole.
E1J3_B_OA
E1J3_B_QA
~z~It's in that multi-storey car park in Purgatory.
~z~You always were the most reliable brother, Johnny. Too cool.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~不愧是我最可靠的兄弟，Johnny。太棒了。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Hey, asshole, you're fucking up my new bike!
~z~Let's get this done.
~z~They got it outside that showroom on Percell in Westdyke.
~z~Why hello.
~z~The bike's there, man. The bike's fucking there.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~摩托有了，兄弟。要的摩托有了。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_C_FA
~z~There's a guy detailing it like he knows it's for sale or something. Outside the tattoo guy in Alderney City.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~车主正在洗车，这不正好要帮他卖车吗。车在Alderney市的纹身店外面。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Looks like I'll be able to afford that hardware I was after. You did good, my brother.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~这下有钱买一直想要的大件了。干得漂亮，好兄弟。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_C_CA
~z~Hey, Deadbeats, I like your bike.
~z~We got one, man. This guy gets mad when they're not delivered, but fuck him, man, you're my brother.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~上次就找过你，兄弟。老板没拿到车气得暴跳如雷。但是去他妈的，你才是我兄弟。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Smoochy time's over, guys. Give up the ride.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~甜蜜时光结束了，各位。交出摩托。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Johnny, man. We haven't been able to source any. It's only a matter of time though so call back.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~Johnny兄弟，暂时没有看中的车。但早晚会找到目标的，有空再聊。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~I ordered a bike, shithead. Give it up.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~这辆摩托我要了，傻蛋。交出车子。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~I'll pass on the good news, Johnny. Later on.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~我会转达这个好消息的，Johnny。再见。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~That last one's in the container heading east and we've lined up another.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~上次的车已经装箱去往远东了。这是新的目标。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Let's do this.
E1J3_C_MA
E1J3_C_BA
~z~I might take that bike off your hands, Deadbeats.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~你们手里的那辆摩托我要了，死妈天使。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Well, you didn't get the last one, but who cares, right? There's another one lined up for you.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~上次你就失手了，但也没关系。新的目标已经给你安排好了。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_C_OA
E1J3_C_DA
~z~I'm taking a bike. Don't be a jackass.
~z~There's nothing available right now, Johnny. Call back soon and we'll see if we can find one.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~现在什么活都没有，Johnny。过会儿再来问问有没有目标吧。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~The guy's happy with the last one and he's hungry for another, man.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~老板对上次的车很满意，急着要下一辆呢，兄弟。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Some Deadbeats are taking it over the East Borough Bridge.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~一些死妈天使正骑着它通过东区大桥。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_B_RJ
~z~Yo, brother.
~z~It's outside the Triangle Club in Bohan. Just bring it back to the House, OK?
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~车在Bohan的三角俱乐部外面。到手了就送回会所，懂了吗？

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~That's cool, brother. Look after yourself.
~z~After delivering like you did before, this dude is happy to be in business with us, man.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~上次你完美交差，现在老板很乐意跟我们合作，兄弟。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Hey man, I can't do that delivery anymore. Hope that's okay?
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，兄弟，我现在没法弄车了。没问题吧？

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Nothing right now, man. Sorry. Call back, okay?
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~什么活都没有，兄弟。抱歉。以后再问，好吗？

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Get a fucking room, kids.
~z~Nice one, brother. We got ourselves a payday.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~干得漂亮，兄弟。我们赚大发了。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Rock and roll.
SFX_PAUSE_600
~z~Brother.
~z~Angus, dude, I gotta postpone getting that bike. Hope that's cool?
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~Angus兄弟，车子我得晚点去弄了。没关系吧？

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~How about that? You just keep knocking 'em out. And you know what? We got another bike lined up.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~这么说吧，你继续保持就行了。知道吗？又有新订单了。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~If it ain't my true brother.
~z~How about that, man. We haven't been able to find what we need. Call again soon and they'll be one.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~这么说吧，兄弟。我们还没找到目标。过段时间应该就有了。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Johnny boy. This import export guy - he's got a long shopping list.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~Johnny仔。这位进出口商的采购清单还挺长的。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Angus, brother. If you were going to export a bike to Japan, where might I be able to find it?
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~Angus，兄弟。假如你要向日本出口摩托，我得去哪儿找车？

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Hey dude, your man isn't going to get his ride. Let him down easy.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，哥们。你老板拿不到摩托车了。让他放宽心吧。

E1J3AUD.original: E1J3_B_RF
~z~On it.
E1J3_C_KA
~z~Alright, man. Your dude's got his bike.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~好了，兄弟。你的人已经拿到车了。

E1J3AUD.original: ~z~Jonathan?
~z~Angus, man, you and your contact are now the proud owners of a second hand bike.
E1J3AUD.translated: ~z~Angus，兄弟，你和你的上家现在是二手车的荣誉车主了。
